      <title>塞文特伦特英镑债券通过水务公司债务需求测试</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/severn-trent-pound-bond-passes-demand-test-for-water-firms-debt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国水务公司塞文特伦特股份有限公司 (Severn Trent Plc) 的英镑债券发售获得了强劲需求，这对陷入困境的英国水务行业来说是一个利好消息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/severn-trent-pound-bond-passes-demand-test-for-water-firms-debt</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 13:28:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
